data.text:
Leatherbox (formerly known as "Het Leerkwartier") is an international online wholesale for premium leather, zippers, hardware and tools for leatherworking. We offer products from the best tanneries and suppliers, because we believe that the quality of international fashion labels should also be accessible to the (semi) professional hobbyist and designer. This is how we ensure that your designs are guaranteed to impress. Visit our webshop, or visit our store in Woerden (The Netherlands). Our quality is your guarantee. Our fresh approach our trademark.
